plot: Oliver Atton wants to be a football professional player. But he has got two rivals, Benji Price, the best goalkeper in Japan, and Mark Lenders, one of the best players. This three are going to play against other countries, and their objective is to win the cup of the world.   Written by  Francisco Silva
